</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>Try this.&nbsp; It's not the most effective way to xp but it can be done.&nbsp;&nbsp; Have 2 healers and one mage.&nbsp;&nbsp; Sick pet on desired mob.&nbsp; Have one healer in group an and one out.&nbsp; Have the one in the group heal the pet for as much as necessary.&nbsp; Then switch that one out for cleric number 2 and pull X amount of mobs more that the pet can tank and have cleric 2 *who is now in gruop*&nbsp; cleric *1 is OoC regening* heal as much as necessary then switch out again.&nbsp; Not the most efficient but if you're pulling 3 mobs give it a shot.&nbsp; Was talking with a mage buddy of mine yesterday and that's what he does.&nbsp; Rinse repeat&nbsp;&nbsp; (prior to the patch).&nbsp; OoC regen.&nbsp; Not only that..if the cleric outside of group has to heal the pet....no aggro FTW!<p>Message Edited by Wingz83 on <span class=date_text>12-11-2006</span> <span class=time_text>08:28 PM</span>
				
