				<DIV>Just a note on pet as a tank.&nbsp; Soloing it works well, or duo with a healer.&nbsp; And full pet groups can do some incredible damage.&nbsp; That said, a pet cannot compete with a real tank at most levels.&nbsp; I am a mid end raider (Anguish/DP guild) and have an Anguish level pet focus.&nbsp; As such my Air pet well buffed/equipped probably is around 16-17k hp (and earth if I used it could probably get above 20k).</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
